data.title: MR. & MRS. Atwood
data.description: 92-acre Tuscan-inspired estate offering indoor and outdoor event spaces, as well as a Four Diamond inn and renowned restaurant.

data.title: MR. MRS Redmond
data.description: Mountain beauty meets warm sophistication at this resort, which boasts a luxury lodge, chic hotel, two country clubs, and plenty of indoor and outdoor wedding venues from refined ballrooms to lush gardens to shabby-chic wood pavilions.

data.title: MR. MRS  Graham
data.description: Faithful replica of a classic medieval castle, complete with turrets, a drawbridge, a vast collection of Medieval and Renaissance artifacts, and a romantic garden overlooking the Atlantic.

data.title: MR. MRS. Yorke
data.description: Fairy-tale Tudor Revival mansion and lakeside chapel surrounded by 100 acres of formal gardens and 900 acres of natural woodlands.

data.title: MR. & MRS. Pearson
data.description: Beautifully restored historic home with elegant indoor event spaces, a Parterre Garden, and a lovely courtyard strung with market lights that's perfect for intimate celebrations.

data.title: MR. & MRS. Raftery
data.description: Relaxed and refined private complex on 24 acres along the Carmel River where you can wed, dine, and stay.

data.title: MR. & MRS. Brower
data.description: Exchange vows in a natural woodland “cathedral” surrounded by towering pines, followed by cocktails served from a charming tipi and a delightful tented reception in the heart of the woods.

data.title: MR. & MRS. Reid
data.description: Romantic 1929 Art Deco, blufftop mansion with indoor and outdoor event venues that offer fantastic ocean and shoreline views.

data.title: MR. & MRS. Squires
data.description: Magnificent 102-acre coastal resort on a bluff overlooking the stunning Palos Verdes Peninsula, boasting landscaped grounds, verdant lawns, and warm, elegant ballrooms with terraces—all with jaw-dropping views.

data.title: MR. & MRS. Jones
data.description: Relaxed, full-service resort presents an alluring choices of indoor and outdoor venues, from al fresco ceremonies with sweeping Pacific vistas to luxe reception ballrooms with classic columns and hand-blown glass chandeliers.
data.location: Hyatt Regency Huntington Beach Resort and Spa

data.title: MR. & MRS. Russell
data.description: This Rockies hideaway boasts incredible mountain vistas and streamside paths, with multiple venue options for al fresco events, from the Shaker, an open-air platform tented with sailcloth, to the Highbanker Beach, a creekside lounge area perfect for cocktails and bonfires.

data.title: MR. & MRS. Smith
data.description: This rustic farmstead getaway offers picture-perfect event spaces, including a hilltop pergola and the Chimney Pond Meadow, surrounded by neat rows of Christmas trees, and a stylishly rustic reception barn highlighted by Tuscan lights and globe chandeliers.
